      "description": "This car is in fair condition. The exterior shows noticeable wear including minor dents, scratches, and some paint fading in areas. The interior has visible wear on the upholstery and surfaces. Mechanically the car runs adequately but shows its age with some minor issues. Suitable for a buyer looking for basic reliable transportation without expecting a pristine vehicle.",
